import React, {Component} from "react" import "../styles/App.css" import "../styles/UserData.css" const imageLink = "https://a.ppy.sh/" const countryFlag = "https://osu.ppy.sh/images/flags/" export default class UserData extends Component { render() { const data = this.props.info console.log(data) const userImage = imageLink + data["user_id"] + "?.jpeg" const userName = data["username"] const globalRank = data["pp_rank"] const countryRank = data["pp_country_rank"] return (
{userName} Global Ranking
{globalRank}
) } }
